AppSync provide:
-access data from one or more data sources from single graphql API endpoint.
-Combine mutiple resources Graphql API into single/ merged graphql API.
-publish real time data update
-built-in secure, monitoring, logging, tracing, with optional cache with low latency.
- only pay for API request and real time msg transfer.

AppSync Events: 
-create secure and performant serverless WebSocket APIs
-no API code required to get starte
-can create production-ready real-time web and mobile experiences in minutes.
- the management and scaling of real-time applications by shifting tasks --> message transformation, broadcast, publish, subscribe authentication and logs, low latency.

With Event APIs, enable the following network communication types.
-Unicast
-Multicast
-Broadcast
-Batch publishing and messaging

